"The KDIGO definition is based on the RIFLE (Risk, Injury, Failure, Loss, and ESKD) and AKIN (Acute Kidney Injury Network) criteria."
],
[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"sup",
"attrs":{
},
"children":[
